9. Advantages

* Easy comparison of algorithms
* Helps understand search strategies
* Modular and extensible design
* Useful for learning AI concepts

10. Limitations

* Hill climbing may fail to find solution
* DFS may not give optimal result
* AO* not implemented (basic version)
* Requires correct heuristic for A*
* entering the state search graph/ tree is quite complete one mistake might lead to a huge error.

11. Future Enhancements

